      "text": "Stack: whisper.cpp v1.8.4 | CUDA 13.2 | Unreal Engine 5.7 | Windows\n• Whisper ggml-small multilingual (99 languages, ~466 MB, ~1 GB VRAM)\n• Auto language detection — bilingual speakers just work\n• Two Whisper passes: transcribe + translate (one model, no cloud)\n• Simple JSON to client: {\"speaker\", \"locale\", \"text\"}",
