      "originalText": "Stack: whisper.cpp v1.8.4 | CUDA 13.2 | Unreal Engine 5.7 | Windows\n• Whisper ggml-small multilingual model (99 languages, ~466 MB)\n• ~1 GB VRAM on GPU — rest free for the game\n• Two Whisper passes per audio: transcribe + translate (one model, no cloud)\n• TCP wire protocol: [locale][audio] → [JSON broadcast]",
